  "detailed_description": "A colorful physics game about caring for your friends.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484600/extras/e5b20644117ba4bd4ca18012b26024f8.poster.avif?t=1736558795\" width=640 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484600/extras/e5b20644117ba4bd4ca18012b26024f8.webm?t=1736558795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484600/extras/e5b20644117ba4bd4ca18012b26024f8.mp4?t=1736558795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484600/extras/23d8b81520b509ce0888b53e3db9bfc5.webp?t=1736558795\" width=640 height=29 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484600/extras/51e7405f8c6731ecefe1a9df286da338.webp?t=1736558795\" width=282 height=60 /></span><br><br>In Stand By Me, play as the curious and adventurous Pico as he travels through a fantastic and ever-changing geometric land with the aid of its many magnetic denizens – and help him find at long last what he's searching for.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484600/extras/ff049dfbb91f1019c00d44240670e69b.poster.avif?t=1736558795\" width=640 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484600/extras/ff049dfbb91f1019c00d44240670e69b.webm?t=1736558795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484600/extras/ff049dfbb91f1019c00d44240670e69b.mp4?t=1736558795\" type=\"video/